{"tid":1778622,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★外媒】iOS 13.3 正式版更新：升級災情回報","createTime":"2019-12-11T05:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T03:56:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"1a77cbcda86819f4a400d250ba41a6451da330fa","tid":1778622,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:42:43.000Z","msg":"蘋果在今天（11）釋出 iOS13.3 正式版本的更新，iOS 13 自從推出過後，維持著極高的更新頻率，每一次的更新都在「滅火」忙著修復先前版本的 bug；即使已經到了 iOS 13.3 版本，也仍然有相當多的災情待解決，不曉得這次是否已經成功修復，除了請大家利用下方表格回報外，也可以至蘋果仁社團討論<br />\n<br />\n<strong>iOS 13.3 之前的災情主要為「LINE 來電鈴聲不響」、「熱點中斷」，根據先前的回報，這兩個最嚴重的災情在 iOS 13.2.3 也沒有修復，因此 iOS 13.3 是否能夠改進就相當值得關注。除了 bug 修復外，iOS 13.3 也推出了部分新功能，大家可以一起來了解。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://applealmond.com/posts/63779\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapplealmond.com%2Fposts%2F63779&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwrccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=2f98b249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://applealmond.com/posts/63779</a>"},{"pid":"e6b9805e65e599d31739af013817bfc541c57fe5","tid":1778622,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f10792efadc3b9404c61680d63da5f8dab87b2","tid":1778622,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":63,"score":-63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:43:14.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"7f6f0d3f4b465ff4016889085fa4105f1ee4c63d","tid":1778622,"uid":263680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy